		"§6Challenge: Gold is expensive in machines, logistics, and powered crafting.§r"
		" "
		"§fProduce or gather 256 Gold Ingots through your automated resource setup.§r"
		" "
		"§7If this takes a while, that is fine: the point is to let the system work for you.§r"
	]
	quest.47BE189106F666DD.quest_subtitle: "Automation Check"
	quest.47BE189106F666DD.title: "Generate Gold"
	quest.47F92CA7E0294DDA.quest_desc: [
		"Begin with the desires centered on caring for bees and their home."
		" "
		"Breed bees, build hives, drink honey, and feed the colony. Check the Bumblezone advancement tab for exact counters."
	]
	quest.47F92CA7E0294DDA.quest_subtitle: "Care for the Colony"
	quest.47F92CA7E0294DDA.title: "The Queen's Beekeeping"
	quest.48AAD65FFE4AE1FF.quest_desc: ["Honey Seeds bottle the sweetness of bees into a calmer, crop-based resource path."]
