		"§fGive it rotation and place blocks in front of its head. Mount it on contraptions when you are ready for mobile mining.§r"
	]
	quest.5B4350BB46637173.quest_subtitle: "Powered Breaking"
	quest.5B4350BB46637173.title: "Craft a Mechanical Drill"
	quest.5C0F21A11B1611E1.quest_desc: ["Let Stone Seeds cover the constant need for cobble, stone, and early building essence."]
	quest.5C0F21A11B1611E1.quest_subtitle: "Cultivated Stone Essence"
	quest.5C0F21A11B1611E1.title: "Stone Seeds"
	quest.5C449B5BAB66086E.quest_desc: ["Sculk Seeds carry deep ancient growth into controlled essence production."]
	quest.5C449B5BAB66086E.quest_subtitle: "Cultivated Sculk Essence"
	quest.5C449B5BAB66086E.title: "Sculk Seeds"
	quest.5D8FC161AF681FD4.quest_desc: ["Turtle Seeds carry slow coastal resources into your controlled farm network."]
	quest.5D8FC161AF681FD4.quest_subtitle: "Cultivated Turtle Essence"
	quest.5D8FC161AF681FD4.title: "Turtle Seeds"
	quest.5E4130136133654B.quest_desc: [
		"§7The Item Drain removes fluids from items and supports tidy fluid loops for later automation.§r"
		" "
		"§fDrop filled containers onto it or pass them across with belts to empty them into connected tanks or pipes.§r"
	]
	quest.5E4130136133654B.quest_subtitle: "Drained Clean"
	quest.5E4130136133654B.title: "Craft an Item Drain"
	quest.6015EDC54A6BCEC0.title: "Drawer"
	quest.6048F41AC1218BF5.quest_desc: [
		"§6The Brass Core is the major capstone for advanced Create machinery.§r"
		" "
		"§fOnce this is stable, complex automation becomes much easier to justify: arms, speed control, observers, and automated assembly all open up.§r"
	]
	quest.6048F41AC1218BF5.quest_subtitle: "Advanced Mechanical Core"
	quest.6048F41AC1218BF5.title: "Craft a Brass Core"
	quest.60CFD33DF18A59CC.quest_desc: ["Lapis Lazuli Seeds support enchanting, dyes, and blue-tier crafting without ore runs."]
	quest.60CFD33DF18A59CC.quest_subtitle: "Cultivated Lapis Lazuli Essence"
	quest.60CFD33DF18A59CC.title: "Lapis Lazuli Seeds"
	quest.60F42F2A2B6BF3D4.quest_desc: ["Resonarium Seeds hum with custom energy, ready for the pack's stronger crafting paths."]
	quest.60F42F2A2B6BF3D4.quest_subtitle: "Cultivated Resonarium Essence"
	quest.60F42F2A2B6BF3D4.title: "Resonarium Seeds"
	quest.61493893A4E2DF29.quest_desc: ["Nickel Seeds keep industrial alloy chains supplied when recipes start scaling up."]
	quest.61493893A4E2DF29.quest_subtitle: "Cultivated Nickel Essence"
	quest.61493893A4E2DF29.title: "Nickel Seeds"
	quest.62006D27C12C3402.quest_desc: [
		"§lJEI§r §7will guide you throughout your journey.§r"
		" "
		"[{\"text\":\"Press \",\"color\":\"white\"},{\"keybind\":\"key.jei.showRecipe\",\"color\":\"gold\"},{\"text\":\" while hovering an item to view its recipes.\",\"color\":\"white\"}]"
		"[{\"text\":\"Press \",\"color\":\"white\"},{\"keybind\":\"key.jei.showUses\",\"color\":\"gold\"},{\"text\":\" to see every recipe using the selected item.\",\"color\":\"white\"}]"
		"[{\"text\":\"Hold \",\"color\":\"white\"},{\"keybind\":\"key.sneak\",\"color\":\"gold\"},{\"text\":\" while hovering items for additional details.\",\"color\":\"white\"}]"
		" "
		"§6Many recipes in this modpack have been heavily customized.§r"
		"§cDo not rely entirely on vanilla progression knowledge.§r"
	]
	quest.62006D27C12C3402.title: "JEI is Your Best Friend"
	quest.629860E916A8B1F7.quest_desc: [
		"§6Mechanical Crafters assemble recipes too large or too awkward for a normal crafting grid.§r"
		" "
		"§fPlace them in the shape of the recipe, set the arrows toward an output, and power the network with rotation.§r"
		" "
		"§eUse a Wrench to rotate the crafter arrows.§r"
	]
	quest.629860E916A8B1F7.quest_subtitle: "Automated Assembly"
	quest.629860E916A8B1F7.title: "Craft Mechanical Crafters"
	quest.62F5592C52CD8821.quest_desc: [
		"The Undergarden is not just another cave. It is a whole dimension beneath the world you know."
		" "
		"Enter it and begin gathering what only grows in that darkness."
	]
	quest.62F5592C52CD8821.quest_subtitle: "Below the World"
	quest.62F5592C52CD8821.title: "Enter the Undergarden"
	quest.631750A602DDA817.quest_desc: [
		"Regalium glows with a cleaner, rarer power than most Undergarden materials."
		" "
		"Find a crystal and keep it for later progression."
	]
	quest.631750A602DDA817.quest_subtitle: "Royal Crystal"
	quest.631750A602DDA817.title: "Find Regalium"
	quest.637878425CE55C37.quest_desc: [
		"The Warden is less a boss than a warning."
		" "
		"Defeat one and prove you can survive the path toward Deeper and Darker."
	]
	quest.637878425CE55C37.quest_subtitle: "The Warning Wakes"
	quest.637878425CE55C37.title: "Defeat the Warden"
	quest.63D67DEF525D3D68.title: "Explorer's Compass"
	quest.647C86D465511AA7.quest_desc: ["Coral Seeds bring fragile reef materials into your garden without damaging the ocean."]
	quest.647C86D465511AA7.quest_subtitle: "Cultivated Coral Essence"
	quest.647C86D465511AA7.title: "Coral Seeds"
	quest.650DC2E21CA320A1.quest_desc: ["Spider Seeds weave string and spider drops into your crop network."]
	quest.650DC2E21CA320A1.quest_subtitle: "Cultivated Spider Essence"
	quest.650DC2E21CA320A1.title: "Spider Seeds"
	quest.65194B1780617E2D.quest_desc: [
		"§6The Alternator converts Create rotation into electrical progress.§r"
		" "
		"§fConnect it to your rotational network and prepare the bridge into the Electric Age.§r"
		" "
		"§eThis is the handoff point: your factory is learning a new language.§r"
	]
	quest.65194B1780617E2D.quest_subtitle: "Rotation Becomes Power"
	quest.65194B1780617E2D.title: "Craft an Alternator"
	quest.6523137544744B69.title: "Obsidian Chest"
	quest.657DCCCCD3FE615E.quest_desc: ["Copper Seeds make pipes, coils, and early machine parts easier to mass produce."]
	quest.657DCCCCD3FE615E.quest_subtitle: "Cultivated Copper Essence"
	quest.657DCCCCD3FE615E.title: "Copper Seeds"
	quest.65A746736DC2D8ED.title: "Diamond Construction Stick"
	quest.6655C9EC1E601EB6.quest_desc: [
		"§7Andesite is rough, common, and easy to overlook.§r"
		" "
		"§fBut in this world, it will become the foundation of your first machines.§r"
	]
	quest.6655C9EC1E601EB6.quest_subtitle: "Stone for Machines"
	quest.6655C9EC1E601EB6.title: "Gather Andesite"
	quest.66A0A2094ABCFD5D.quest_desc: [
		"§7Not every mechanism begins with a full ingot.§r"
		" "
		"§fBreak zinc down into nuggets. Small parts often become the key to larger machines.§r"
	]
	quest.66A0A2094ABCFD5D.quest_subtitle: "Small Components"
	quest.66A0A2094ABCFD5D.title: "Craft Zinc Nuggets"
	quest.68908414B84EC7AC.quest_desc: ["Zombie Seeds make rotten flesh and undead resources useful through automation."]
	quest.68908414B84EC7AC.quest_subtitle: "Cultivated Zombie Essence"
	quest.68908414B84EC7AC.title: "Zombie Seeds"
	quest.689AD3F0E7571A85.quest_desc: ["Energite Seeds give your energy-tier materials a renewable backbone."]
	quest.689AD3F0E7571A85.quest_subtitle: "Cultivated Energite Essence"
	quest.689AD3F0E7571A85.title: "Energite Seeds"
	quest.6942D9CB3B07E0D8.title: "Configuration Tool"
	quest.6A4CCCEA030C7865.title: "Controller Extension"
	quest.6AD41FA37188492D.quest_desc: [
		"Complete all sixteen Queen's Desire advancements."
		" "
		"The mod's advancement screen tracks every counter precisely. This final advancement completes automatically when all sixteen are done."
	]
	quest.6AD41FA37188492D.quest_subtitle: "Every Desire Fulfilled"
	quest.6AD41FA37188492D.title: "Reach Journey's End"
	quest.6B7EC1E71863906F.quest_desc: [
		"§6The Wrench is Create's best quality-of-life tool.§r"
		" "
		"§fUse it to rotate, configure, pick up, and clean up Create blocks without rebuilding everything by hand.§r"
	]
	quest.6B7EC1E71863906F.quest_subtitle: "Factory Tuning"
	quest.6B7EC1E71863906F.title: "Craft a Wrench"
	quest.6BA09360A88A9072.quest_desc: [
		"§7The Content Observer reads inventories and signals when conditions are met.§r"
		" "
		"§fPoint it at a container, belt, or depot and use the signal to control smarter automation.§r"
	]
	quest.6BA09360A88A9072.quest_subtitle: "Watchful Automation"
	quest.6BA09360A88A9072.title: "Craft a Content Observer"
	quest.6BB174B968379666.quest_desc: [
		"§7Viridite is a custom material for this pack, used to begin one branch of resource generation.§r"
		" "
		"§fGather 16 Viridite while exploring, then use it to craft its matching core.§r"
		" "
		"§eThe early step is discovery; the reward is not having to repeat that mining forever.§r"
	]
	quest.6BB174B968379666.quest_subtitle: "Exploration Material"
	quest.6BB174B968379666.title: "Gather Viridite"
	quest.6C74B0300D2159A6.quest_desc: [
		"Something is hunting through the silence of the Otherside."
		" "
		"Defeat a Stalker and take back a little control over the dark."
	]
	quest.6C74B0300D2159A6.quest_subtitle: "Hunter in the Dark"
	quest.6C74B0300D2159A6.title: "Defeat a Stalker"
	quest.6CE2C3EFDCA2D25D.title: "Iron Barrel"
	quest.6D407B1D6ECEC401.title: "Diamond Backpack"
	quest.6DF3932CE848E0A1.quest_desc: ["Deepslate Seeds bring the deep stone layer into automation before mining becomes a chore."]
	quest.6DF3932CE848E0A1.quest_subtitle: "Cultivated Deepslate Essence"
	quest.6DF3932CE848E0A1.title: "Deepslate Seeds"
	quest.6DF5162588711E4F.quest_desc: ["Start the real Mystical Agriculture loop with Inferium Seeds, the base of every higher tier."]
	quest.6DF5162588711E4F.quest_subtitle: "Cultivated Inferium Essence"
	quest.6DF5162588711E4F.title: "Inferium Seeds"
	quest.6ED33C26796DEA3A.quest_desc: [
		"§7Every journey begins with something simple.§r"
		" "
		"§fGather any type of log to start building your first tools and shelter.§r"
		" "
		"§6The fractured world will not wait for you.§r"
	]
	quest.6ED33C26796DEA3A.quest_subtitle: "The Beginning"
	quest.6ED33C26796DEA3A.title: "Gather Wood"
	quest.70B1DD16E287E1E0.title: "Diamond Chest"
	quest.716185F216AB4B7E.quest_desc: [
		"Utheric Shards can be formed into a stronger crystal."
		" "
		"Obtain Utherium and continue building your Undergarden material chain."
	]
	quest.716185F216AB4B7E.quest_subtitle: "Crystallized Power"
	quest.716185F216AB4B7E.title: "Make Utherium"
	quest.717A0D8EDE87A2DF.quest_desc: ["Stabilize your first fields with Earth Seeds, turning basic soil work into a steady essence source."]
	quest.717A0D8EDE87A2DF.quest_subtitle: "Cultivated Earth Essence"
	quest.717A0D8EDE87A2DF.title: "Earth Seeds"
	quest.72033845D8A91608.quest_desc: [
		"§6Engineer's Goggles reveal stress, speed, and machine details that are otherwise easy to miss.§r"
		" "
		"§fWear them while looking at Create machines to understand why a setup is slow, overstressed, or disconnected.§r"
	]
	quest.72033845D8A91608.quest_subtitle: "Read the Machines"
	quest.72033845D8A91608.title: "Craft Engineer's Goggles"
	quest.72A610C3E3B1C7AE.quest_desc: ["Nature Seeds gather plant life into one crop, smoothing out dye, leaf, and organic recipes."]
	quest.72A610C3E3B1C7AE.quest_subtitle: "Cultivated Nature Essence"
	quest.72A610C3E3B1C7AE.title: "Nature Seeds"
	quest.72D10B75A011DEB8.title: "Netherite Upgrade"
	quest.72EC9401EE3BA289.quest_desc: [
		"§7Many dimensions, structures, and hidden locations contain important resources, progression items, and fragments of lost knowledge.§r"
		" "
		"§6The world of Fractured Reality rewards curiosity.§r"
		" "
		"§fDo not remain underground forever.§r"
	]
	quest.72EC9401EE3BA289.title: "Exploration is Essential"
	quest.7303890E9D4FFCCF.quest_desc: ["Dirt Seeds are humble, but they make terrain work and bulk crafting much less manual."]
